<dita xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/"><concept id="DFARS_213.302-5" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">213.302-5</ph> Clauses.</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List1">(a) Use the clause at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" class="- topic/xref " base="DFARS-252.243-7001" href="252.243-7001.dita#DFARS_252.243-7001">252.243-7001</xref>, Pricing of Contract Modifications, in all bilateral purchase orders.</p><p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List1"> (d) When using the clause at FAR <xref scope="external" format="html" href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/52.213-4" class="- topic/xref ">52.213-4</xref>, delete the reference to the clause at FAR <xref scope="external" format="html" href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/52.225-1" class="- topic/xref ">52.225-1</xref>, Buy American–Supplies. Instead, if the Buy American <ph class="- topic/ph " rev="Revised February 15, 2024">statute</ph> applies to the acquisition, use the clause at—</p><p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List3"> (i) <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" href="252.225-7001.dita" class="- topic/xref ">252.225-7001</xref>, Buy American and Balance of Payments Program, <ph class="- topic/ph " rev="Revised February 15, 2024">or the appropriate alternate,</ph> as prescribed at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" href="225.1101.dita" class="- topic/xref ">225.1101</xref>(2); or</p><p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List3"> (ii) <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" href="252.225-7036.dita" class="- topic/xref ">252.225-7036</xref>, Buy American –Free Trade Agreements—Balance of Payments Program, <ph class="- topic/ph " rev="Revised February 15, 2024">or the appropriate alternate,</ph> as prescribed at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" href="225.1101.dita" class="- topic/xref ">225.1101</xref>(10).</p></conbody></concept></dita>